        "title_zh": "技术要求",
        "title_en": "",
        "type": "list",
        "content": "<ul><li>1、带★要求，为产品重要和关键特性</li><li>2、引出线不能断开，绝缘层和线芯不能损伤</li><li>3、定子引出线参照GB/T 7345-2008要求</li><li>4、对于定子三相线，每根引出线应能承受9.0N的拉力</li></ul>",
        "content_en": "<ul><li>1. Important and critical feature</li><li>2. Lead, insulation and wire core must not be damaged</li><li>3. Stator leads per GB/T 7345-2008</li><li>4. Lead tensile force 9.0N</li></ul>",
        "text": "技术要求Technicalrequirements:\n1、带★要求，为产品重要和关键特性\nRequirements marked with ★ indicate important and\ncriticalfeatures of the product\n2、引出线不能断开，绝缘层和线芯不能损伤\nThe outgoing line cannot be disconnected, and the\ninsulation layer and wire core cannot be damaged\n3、定子引出线参照GB/T7345-2008要求\nThe stator outgoing line shall comply with the\nrequirementsofGB/T 7345-2008\n4、对于定子三相线，每根引出线应能承受9.0N的拉力\nFor stator three-phase wires,each lead out wire\nshould be able to withstand atensile force of 9.ON",
